room_title: Escape room "Serial Killer" by BreakOut Escape Game in Charleston
room_description: A cruel serial killer has trapped you and your friends in his house to play his unusual games of torture and despair. Now he is testing your basic knowledge to see if you are smart enough to escape the rooms of doom that he has created. You have to use your logic, problem-solving skills and your creativity to survive. You've got only 60 minutes: soon you will realize that time is your worst enemy...
